abstract: It has finally admitted defeat in its bids to block AT&T’s takeover of Time Warner. There are plenty of other fish to fry.

abstract: Policy ideas once dismissed out of hand are now being widely discussed. The Overton window is one way to understand what’s happening.
snippet: Policy ideas once dismissed out of hand are now being widely discussed. The Overton window is one way to understand what’s happening.
lead_paragraph: You may have heard about the Overton window, and that’s not about to stop. With the political landscape shifting in sometimes startling ways, what was once an obscure idea has gained broader relevance.

snippet: She made her debut in Vienna in 1947, a Jew who had fled Hitler, and feared onetime Nazis would disrupt her performance. Instead, they applauded.
lead_paragraph: Hilde Zadek was frightened as she stepped onto the stage. She had every reason to be.
